  Priority Colors
  ---------------
  priority-p1:        #B8860B   (Gold — highest urgency)
  priority-p2:        #D97706   (Amber)
  priority-p3:        #6B21A8   (Violet)
  priority-p4:        #475569   (Slate — lowest)

