  quote-md:      Playfair   500  18px / 26px   letter-spacing: 0px
  quote-sm:      Playfair   400  15px / 22px   letter-spacing: 0px

0.3 SHADOWS (Purple-Tinted — NEVER gray)
-----------------------------------------

  shadow-xs:    0 1px 2px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
  shadow-sm:    0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.06)
  shadow-md:    0 4px 8px rgba(26,5,51,0.06), 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
  shadow-lg:    0 8px 16px rgba(26,5,51,0.08), 0 4px 8px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
  shadow-xl:    0 12px 24px rgba(26,5,51,0.10), 0 8px 12px rgba(26,5,51,0.06)
  shadow-2xl:   0 20px 40px rgba(26,5,51,0.12), 0 12px 16px rgba(26,5,51,0.06)
  shadow-inner: inset 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
  shadow-glow:  0 0 16px rgba(107,33,168,0.12)   (purple glow for focus)
  shadow-gold:  0 0 16px rgba(184,134,11,0.15)    (gold glow for CTAs)

0.4 GLASS MORPHISM (Light Mode)
---------------------------------

  glass-card:
    background:   rgba(255,255,255,0.65)
    backdrop-filter: blur(8px) saturate(1.2)
    border:       1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
    box-shadow:   shadow-md
    border-radius: 16px

  glass-sheet:
    background:   rgba(255,255,255,0.85)
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(1.3)
    border:       1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
    box-shadow:   shadow-lg
    border-radius: 24px 24px 0 0

  glass-pill:
    background:   rgba(255,255,255,0.70)
    backdrop-filter: blur(6px)
    border:       1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.10)
    box-shadow:   shadow-sm
    border-radius: 100px (fully rounded)

0.5 SPACING & LAYOUT
---------------------

  Base unit: 4px
  Spacing scale: 4, 8, 12, 16, 20, 24, 32, 40, 48, 64, 80
  Screen padding (horizontal): 20px
  Card padding: 16px (compact), 20px (standard), 24px (spacious)
  Card gap: 12px (tight), 16px (standard), 20px (loose)
  Border radii: 4px (micro), 8px (sm), 12px (md), 16px (lg), 20px (xl), 24px (2xl), 100px (pill)
  Safe area top: 44px (iPhone notch) / 24px (Android status bar)
  Safe area bottom: 34px (iPhone home) / 16px (Android nav)
  Bottom nav height: 64px + safe area
  App bar height: 56px
  FAB size: 56px
  Touch target minimum: 44px x 44px

0.6 ANIMATION TOKENS
---------------------

  duration-instant:  100ms
  duration-fast:     200ms
  duration-normal:   300ms
  duration-slow:     500ms
  duration-reveal:   800ms
  duration-dramatic: 1200ms
  curve-standard:    cubic-bezier(0.2, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0)   (Material 3 standard)
  curve-decel:       cubic-bezier(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0)    (entering elements)
  curve-accel:       cubic-bezier(0.3, 0.0, 1.0, 1.0)    (exiting elements)
  curve-spring:      cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275)  (bouncy)
  curve-sharp:       cubic-bezier(0.4, 0.0, 0.6, 1.0)    (quick moves)

0.7 DARK -> LIGHT MODE DIFFERENCES (Global)
-------------------------------------------

  WHY we diverge from dark in light mode:
  1. CONTRAST INVERSION: Dark uses light text on dark; light uses dark text on light.
     We boost text-primary to #1A0533 (17.51:1) because light backgrounds demand heavier text.
  2. SHADOW COLOR SHIFT: Gray shadows look dirty on purple-tinted backgrounds.
     Purple-tinted shadows (rgba(26,5,51,x)) feel cohesive and premium.
  3. GLASS OPACITY INCREASE: Dark mode glass = 15-25% white; light mode = 65-85% white.
     Light mode glass needs to be more opaque so content behind does not create illegible text.
  4. GRADIENT REDUCTION: Dark mode uses gradient meshes for depth; light mode uses solid/subtle.
     Gradients on light backgrounds create washed-out, unprofessional feel. Solids look crisper.
  5. ANIMATION PARTICLE OPACITY: Dark = 30-40%; Light = 15-20%.
     Particles are decorative. On light bg they become distracting at dark-mode opacities.
  6. ACCENT VIBRANCY: Gold #B8860B is unchanged but reads darker/richer on light.
     No adjustment needed — the optical illusion of light bg makes gold feel warmer.


================================================================================
A1. SPLASH SCREEN
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Brand reveal, emotional first impression. Load core resources in background.
DURATION: 2.4 seconds total (1.8s animation + 0.6s hold + transition)

VISUAL HIERARCHY
----------------
  1. Background (full screen)
  2. UNJYNX logotype (center, dominant)
  3. Gold accent mark (subtle, on the 'J')
  4. Tagline (below logo, delayed fade)

LAYOUT
------
  Background: #FFFFFF (pure white — cleaner than #F8F5FF for dramatic reveal)
  Full screen, no safe area UI
  Logo centered both axes: centerX, centerY - 20px (slight upward offset for optical center)

LOGOTYPE "UNJYNX"
------------------
  Font: Outfit
  Weight: 800 (ExtraBold)
  Size: 48px
  Letter-spacing: 4px (wide tracking for editorial feel)
  Color: #1A0533 (Midnight Purple — NOT black, brand-specific)
  Text-transform: uppercase

  REVEAL ANIMATION (letter-by-letter ink materialization):
    Each letter appears with an ink-bleed effect:
    - Letter starts as invisible (opacity 0, scale Y 0.3, blur 4px)
    - Ink bleeds in from the baseline upward over 200ms per letter
    - Stagger: 120ms between letters (U->N->J->Y->N->X)
    - Total letter sequence: 120ms * 5 gaps + 200ms = 800ms
    - Easing: curve-decel for each letter

    Ink-feel implementation:
    - Use mask with vertical gradient that slides up
    - Slight overshoot on scaleY (1.0 -> 1.02 -> 1.0) for organic feel
    - Blur removes from 4px -> 0px during reveal
    - Color: starts #3B0764 (deeper), settles to #1A0533 (final)

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: In dark mode, text is #F8F5FF (light) on #0A0118 (dark).
    Light mode uses #1A0533 on #FFFFFF for maximum editorial contrast.
    The ink-bleed reads as "writing on paper" in light mode vs "glowing reveal" in dark.

GOLD ACCENT ON 'J'
-------------------
  The top hook of the 'J' gets a gold accent:
  - Color: #B8860B
  - Applied as a gradient overlay on just the top 40% of the J letterform
  - Appears 200ms after the J letter completes its ink reveal
  - Fade in: 300ms, curve-decel
  - Subtle gold shimmer: 0 0 8px rgba(184,134,11,0.20) glow pulses once

TAGLINE (appears after logo is complete)
-----------------------------------------
  Text: "Break the satisfactory."
  Font: DM Sans
  Weight: 400
  Size: 14px / 20px
  Letter-spacing: 2px
  Text-transform: uppercase
  Color: #6B21A8 (Deep Violet)
  Position: centered, 24px below logo baseline
  Animation: fade in 0 -> 1 opacity over 400ms, starts at t=1200ms
  Easing: curve-decel

TRANSITION TO APP (t=1800ms -> t=2400ms)
-----------------------------------------
  The logo and tagline perform a coordinated exit:
  1. Tagline fades out first (200ms, opacity 1 -> 0)
  2. Logo scales down: 48px -> target app bar size (20px)
  3. Logo translates from center to app bar title position:
     - Destination: top-left, x=20px from left, y=safe-area-top + 16px
  4. Background crossfades: #FFFFFF -> #F8F5FF (Purple Mist) over 400ms
  5. Main UI elements begin to fade in below as logo reaches destination
  Duration: 600ms total transition
  Easing: curve-standard (smooth, not bouncy)

  IMPLEMENTATION NOTE: Use Hero animation (Flutter) with flightShuttleBuilder
  to morph the splash logo into the persistent app bar title.

LOADING INDICATOR (optional, if resources not ready)
----------------------------------------------------
  Only shown if load > 2.4s
  Position: bottom center, 80px above bottom edge
  Three dots: 6px circles, #6B21A8, opacity pulse 0.3 -> 1.0
  Stagger: 200ms between dots
  Animation: infinite loop until ready


================================================================================
A2. LOGIN / SIGN-UP SCREEN
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Authentication entry point. Build trust, show brand personality.
LAYOUT: Single scrollable screen with fixed background.

VISUAL HIERARCHY
----------------
  1. Background atmosphere
  2. App logo + tagline (top section)
  3. Glass auth card (center, dominant)
  4. Social login buttons (inside card)
  5. OR divider
  6. Email/password fields (inside card)
  7. CTA button (inside card, bottom)
  8. Legal text (below card)

BACKGROUND
----------
  Base: #F8F5FF (Purple Mist)
  Radial gradient overlay (centered, decorative):
    Center: rgba(107,33,168,0.04) (barely visible purple)
    Edge: rgba(107,33,168,0.00) (transparent)
    Radius: 70% of screen width
    Position: center of screen, vertically offset -10% (slightly above center)

  WHY subtle gradient: Creates depth without competing with the glass card.
  In dark mode, gradient is more visible (0.08 opacity) because dark bg absorbs more.
  Light mode needs restraint — too much gradient looks washed out.

TOP SECTION (Logo + Tagline)
-----------------------------
  Position: top of scroll, centered
  Padding top: safe-area + 48px
  Padding bottom: 32px

  Logo "UNJYNX":
    Font: Outfit 800, 32px, letter-spacing 3px, uppercase
    Color: #1A0533
    Gold accent on J: #B8860B (same as splash)

  Tagline:
    "Break the satisfactory. Unjynx your productivity."
    Font: DM Sans 400, 14px / 20px, letter-spacing 0.5px
    Color: #1A0533
    Gold underline beneath "Unjynx your productivity":
      Height: 2px
      Color: #B8860B
      Width: matches text width + 4px padding each side
      Offset: 4px below text baseline
      Border-radius: 1px
    Margin top: 8px below logo

GLASS AUTH CARD
---------------
  Position: centered horizontally, below top section
  Width: min(375px, screen-width - 40px)  [20px padding each side]
  Padding: 32px horizontal, 28px vertical
  Background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85)
  Backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(1.3)
  Border: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
  Border-radius: 24px
  Box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(26,5,51,0.08), 0 4px 12px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)

  WHY 85% white glass (vs 25% in dark): Light mode glass must be mostly opaque
  to maintain text legibility. The 15% transparency creates a subtle frosted effect
  without sacrificing readability. Purple-tinted shadow grounds it on the #F8F5FF bg.

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Dark uses rgba(26,5,51,0.40) bg with blur(16px).
  Light mode inverts to high-white opacity. The border tint is the same purple
  but reads as barely-there on light, vs visible boundary on dark.

SOCIAL LOGIN BUTTONS (inside card)
-----------------------------------
  Layout: vertical stack, 12px gap
  Each button:
    Width: 100%
    Height: 52px
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Border: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
    Border-radius: 12px
    Box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.06)
    Padding: 0 16px

    Icon: provider's official full-color icon, 24px x 24px, left-aligned
    Text: DM Sans 500, 15px, #1A0533, center-aligned with icon offset
    Gap between icon and text: 12px

    Hover/Press state:
      Background: #F0EAFC
      Box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(26,5,51,0.08)
      Transition: 150ms curve-standard

    Providers (top to bottom):
      1. Google — Google 'G' multicolor icon — "Continue with Google"
      2. Apple — Apple icon #1A0533 (not black) — "Continue with Apple"
      3. GitHub — GitHub Octocat #1A0533 — "Continue with GitHub"

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Social buttons in dark use rgba(255,255,255,0.06) bg
  with white text. Light mode uses full white cards for clarity and trust.

OR DIVIDER
----------
  Position: centered, 24px above and below
  Line: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08), extends to card edges (minus padding)
  Text: "OR", DM Sans 500, 12px, letter-spacing 2px, #475569
  Background behind "OR": #FFFFFF (matches card bg to "cut" the line)
  Padding: 0 12px around text

EMAIL / PASSWORD FIELDS
------------------------
  Layout: vertical stack, 16px gap

  Text Input Field:
    Width: 100%
    Height: 52px
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Border: 1.5px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.12)
    Border-radius: 12px
    Padding: 0 16px

    Label (floating):
      Font: DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569 (unfocused)
      Font: DM Sans 500, 12px, #6B21A8 (focused, floated above)
      Transition: 200ms curve-standard

    Input text: DM Sans 400, 16px, #1A0533
    Placeholder: DM Sans 400, 16px, #94A3B8

    Focus state:
      Border: 1.5px solid #6B21A8
      Box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(107,33,168,0.08) (focus ring)
      Label color: #6B21A8

    Error state:
      Border: 1.5px solid #E11D48
      Box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(225,29,72,0.08)
      Error text: DM Sans 400, 12px, #E11D48, 4px below field

    Password field additions:
      Visibility toggle icon: right side, 24px, #475569
      Tap target: 44px x 44px
      Toggled icon color: #6B21A8

  Forgot Password link:
    Position: right-aligned below password field, 8px below
    Font: DM Sans 500, 13px, #6B21A8
    Tap target: 44px height (padded)
    Underline on press: 1px #6B21A8

CTA BUTTON
----------
  Position: below fields, 24px margin top
  Width: 100%
  Height: 56px
  Background: #B8860B (Brand Gold)
  Border-radius: 14px
  Box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(184,134,11,0.25), 0 2px 4px rgba(184,134,11,0.15)

  Text: "Sign In" or "Create Account" (toggled)
  Font: DM Sans 700, 16px, #FFFFFF (4.8:1 contrast on gold)
  Letter-spacing: 0.5px

  Hover/Press:
    Background: #A07608 (darker gold)
    Box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(184,134,11,0.30)
    Scale: 0.98 (press), 1.0 (release, spring curve 200ms)

  Loading state:
    Text replaced with circular spinner
    Spinner: 20px, stroke 2px, #FFFFFF
    Background: #B8860B (unchanged, button not disabled visually)

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Same gold color. Dark mode adds a subtle glow
  (0 0 20px rgba(184,134,11,0.30)) that light mode omits because glow
  is invisible on light backgrounds.

SIGN IN <-> SIGN UP TOGGLE
--------------------------
  Position: below CTA, 16px margin top, centered
  Text: "Don't have an account? Sign Up" (or inverse)
  Font: DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569 for question, DM Sans 600, 14px, #6B21A8 for action
  Tap target: full line width, 44px height

LEGAL TEXT
----------
  Position: below glass card, 24px margin top, centered
  Width: matches card width
  Text: "By continuing, you agree to our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy"
  Font: DM Sans 400, 12px / 18px, #475569
  Links ("Terms of Service", "Privacy Policy"): #6B21A8, underline on press
  Tap target per link: 44px height (padded)

ENTRY ANIMATION
----------------
  1. Background: instant (already loaded from splash transition)
  2. Logo + tagline: fade in, translateY -20px -> 0, 400ms, curve-decel (t=0)
  3. Glass card: fade in, translateY 30px -> 0, 500ms, curve-decel (t=100ms)
  4. Social buttons: stagger in, 100ms between, translateY 10px -> 0, 300ms (t=300ms)
  5. Fields + CTA: fade in, 300ms (t=500ms)


================================================================================
B1-B4. ONBOARDING CAROUSEL (4 SCREENS)
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Educate new users about core value props. Capture initial preferences.
LAYOUT: Full-screen carousel with fixed bottom controls.

GLOBAL CAROUSEL STRUCTURE
--------------------------
  Swipe: horizontal paging
  Skip button: top-right, DM Sans 500, 14px, #475569, tap target 44px x 44px
  Position: safe-area-top + 12px, right 20px

  Page indicator (Chain Link Progress):
    Position: bottom, 120px above bottom edge (above CTA)
    4 chain links, each 32px wide x 8px tall, 8px gap
    Inactive chain: 2px border #6B21A8 at 30% opacity, transparent fill, border-radius 4px
    Active chain: solid #6B21A8 fill, border-radius 4px
    Transition between: the link "breaks" — the chain splits with a 2px gap, and a gold
    spark particle (#B8860B) bursts from the break point (4 particles, 6px, fade over 400ms)
    Break animation: 300ms, curve-spring

    WHY chain metaphor: "Unjynx" = breaking chains of mediocrity. Each completed
    onboarding slide is a broken chain — the gold spark is the "unjynxing" moment.

  CTA Button (bottom):
    Position: 20px from each side, bottom safe-area + 20px
    Width: calc(100% - 40px)
    Height: 56px
    Slides 1-3: "Next" — ghost style:
      Background: transparent
      Border: 2px solid #6B21A8
      Text: DM Sans 600, 16px, #6B21A8
      Border-radius: 14px
    Slide 4: "Get Started" — gold CTA:
      Background: #B8860B
      Text: DM Sans 700, 16px, #FFFFFF
      Box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(184,134,11,0.25)
      Border-radius: 14px

SLIDE B1: "Your Tasks, Everywhere" (Core Task Management)
----------------------------------------------------------
  Background gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #F8F5FF 0%, #F0EAFC 100%)

  ILLUSTRATION (top 45% of screen):
    Centered illustration at 280px x 280px
    Content: Stylized phone showing task list with floating task cards around it
    Style: flat with purple (#6B21A8) outlines, gold (#B8860B) accent on checkbox ticks
    Cards have white fill + purple-tinted shadow
    Animation: floating cards gently bob up/down (translateY +/- 4px, 3s loop, curve-standard)

  HEADLINE:
    Position: centered, below illustration, 24px gap
    Text: "Your Tasks, Everywhere"
    Font: Outfit 700, 28px / 34px, #1A0533
    Letter-spacing: -0.3px

  BODY:
    Position: centered, 12px below headline
    Width: min(320px, screen-width - 64px)
    Text: "Organize, prioritize, and crush your to-do list with an app that adapts to how you work."
    Font: DM Sans 400, 16px / 24px, #475569
    Text-align: center

SLIDE B2: "Reach Them Anywhere" (Channel Showcase)
----------------------------------------------------
  Background gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #F8F5FF 0%, #EDE5F7 100%)
  Slightly deeper lavender to differentiate from B1.

  ILLUSTRATION (top 45%):
    280px x 280px centered
    Content: Central hub with lines radiating to channel icons:
      WhatsApp (green), Telegram (blue), Email (red/orange),
      SMS (purple), Instagram (gradient), Discord (indigo), Slack (multicolor)
    Hub: gold (#B8860B) circle, 48px, with bell icon inside
    Channel icons: 32px each, full official colors, arranged in circle around hub
    Connecting lines: 1.5px, #6B21A8 at 30% opacity
    Animation: lines pulse from center to icons (gold -> purple gradient traveling along line),
    staggered 200ms each, continuous 4s loop

  HEADLINE:
    "Reach Them Anywhere"
    Font: Outfit 700, 28px / 34px, #1A0533

  BODY:
    "Send reminders through WhatsApp, Telegram, email, SMS — wherever people actually check."
    Font: DM Sans 400, 16px / 24px, #475569, centered, max-width 320px

SLIDE B3: "Smart Enough to Surprise You" (AI Features)
--------------------------------------------------------
  Background gradient: linear-gradient(180deg, #F8F5FF 0%, #FFF8E1 100%)
  Gold wash creates warmth for AI/intelligence messaging.

  ILLUSTRATION (top 45%):
    280px x 280px centered
    Content: Crystal ball (deep violet #3B0764 outer, lighter gradient inner)
    with floating insight cards emerging from it
    Insight cards: white, 8px radius, purple shadow, containing mini text lines
    One card has a gold (#B8860B) lightbulb icon
    Animation: crystal ball has subtle inner shimmer (radial gradient rotation, 6s),
    insight cards float up from ball and fade (translateY -40px, opacity 1 -> 0, stagger 1.5s)

  HEADLINE:
    "Smart Enough to Surprise You"
    Font: Outfit 700, 28px / 34px, #1A0533

  BODY:
    "AI that learns your patterns, predicts what you need, and nudges you at exactly the right moment."
    Font: DM Sans 400, 16px / 24px, #475569, centered, max-width 320px

SLIDE B4: "What Drives You?" (Preference Selection — Interactive)
------------------------------------------------------------------
  Background: solid #F8F5FF (no gradient — interactive screen stays clean)

  HEADLINE:
    Position: top, safe-area + 60px
    "What Drives You?"
    Font: Outfit 700, 28px / 34px, #1A0533, centered

  SUBHEAD:
    "Pick 3+ categories to personalize your experience"
    Font: DM Sans 400, 14px / 20px, #475569, centered, 8px below headline

  CATEGORY GRID:
    Position: 24px below subhead, horizontal padding 20px
    Layout: 3 columns, 12px gap
    Scroll: vertical if needed

    Category Card (unselected):
      Width: (screen-width - 40px - 24px) / 3 = ~105px at 375px screen
      Height: 96px
      Background: #FFFFFF
      Border: 1.5px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.10)
      Border-radius: 12px
      Box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
      Layout: centered vertical stack
        Icon: 28px, color #6B21A8
        Label: DM Sans 500, 12px, #1A0533, 6px below icon
      Tap target: entire card

    Category Card (selected):
      Background: #FFF8E1 (Gold Wash)
      Border: 2px solid #B8860B
      Box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(184,134,11,0.12)
      Icon color: #B8860B
      Label color: #1A0533 (unchanged)
      Checkmark: 16px gold (#B8860B) circle in top-right corner of card,
        4px from edges, with white checkmark icon 10px inside
      Transition: all 200ms curve-spring (slight bounce on select)

    Categories (12 shown, scroll for more):
      Work, Personal, Health, Finance, Learning, Social,
      Creative, Travel, Shopping, Family, Fitness, Mindfulness

  MINIMUM INDICATOR:
    Position: centered, 16px below grid
    Text: "3 of 3+ selected" or "1 of 3+ selected"
    Font: DM Sans 500, 13px, color changes:
      < 3 selected: #E11D48 (needs more)
      >= 3 selected: #059669 (good to go)

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Category cards in dark use rgba(255,255,255,0.06) bg.
    Selected = rgba(184,134,11,0.15) fill with gold border.
    Light mode uses clean white cards with the warm gold wash on selection,
    which reads as a gentle highlight rather than dark mode's ember glow.


================================================================================
C1. HOME SCREEN (MOST IMPORTANT SCREEN)
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Daily command center. Must feel calm yet informative. Clear hierarchy.
LAYOUT: Scrollable column with fixed bottom nav + optional FAB.

VISUAL HIERARCHY (TOP TO BOTTOM)
----------------------------------
  1. App bar (greeting + avatar)
  2. Streak + progress summary
  3. Daily content card
  4. Quick actions row
  5. Task sections (Today, Upcoming, Overdue)
  6. AI Whisper card (contextual)
  7. Bottom navigation

BACKGROUND
----------
  Solid #F8F5FF (Purple Mist)
  NO gradient mesh (unlike dark mode which uses multi-stop radial gradients)

  WHY no gradient: Light mode benefits from clean, solid backgrounds.
  Gradient meshes on light bg create an "unfinished watercolor" effect.
  Solid #F8F5FF gives a paper-like quality — editorial, calm, premium.

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Dark uses a 3-stop radial gradient mesh
  (#0A0118 base + purple and violet spots) for immersive depth.
  Light mode achieves depth through shadows and card elevation instead.

APP BAR
-------
  Height: 56px (content) + safe-area-top
  Background: transparent (scrolls with content, no elevation until scroll)
  Padding: 0 20px

  Left side:
    Greeting text:
      "Good morning, Rahul" (time-contextual: morning/afternoon/evening/night)
      Font: Outfit 600, 20px / 26px, #1A0533
      Truncate with ellipsis if name > 12 characters

    Date:
      "Monday, March 10"
      Font: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569
      Margin-top: 2px

  Right side:
    Avatar: 40px x 40px circle
      Background: #EDE5F7 (if no image)
      Initials: Outfit 600, 16px, #6B21A8
      If image: cover fill, 40px circle
      Border: 2px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.10)
      Tap -> profile/settings

  On scroll (past 20px):
    Background: rgba(248,245,255,0.95) (almost opaque Purple Mist)
    Backdrop-filter: blur(8px)
    Border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
    Box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
    Transition: 200ms curve-standard

STREAK & PROGRESS SECTION
--------------------------
  Position: 16px below app bar
  Padding: 0 20px

  Streak Row:
    Layout: horizontal, space-between alignment
    Left: streak info
    Right: progress rings

    Streak Flame (Rive animation):
      Size: 48px x 48px
      Flame colors: #FF6B00 base, #FFB800 mid, #B8860B tips
      Animation: continuous flicker, 2-3 flame layers
      WHY richer on light: Real flames are more visible in daylight.
      Dark mode flames glow against the dark (additive blending).
      Light mode flames are opaque, solid — like a candle in a bright room.
      Use normal blend mode (not additive/screen as in dark mode).

    Streak Text (right of flame, 12px gap):
      Count: Bebas Neue 400, 48px, #1A0533 ("7")
      Label: DM Sans 500, 13px, #475569 ("day streak")
      Layout: vertical stack, 0px gap

    Progress Rings (right side):
      3 concentric rings, right-aligned
      Container: 72px x 72px

      Outer ring (Tasks completed):
        Diameter: 72px, stroke width: 6px
        Track: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
        Fill: #B8860B (Gold) — clockwise from 12 o'clock
        Cap: round

      Middle ring (Focus minutes):
        Diameter: 56px, stroke width: 5px
        Track: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
        Fill: #8B5CF6 (Violet)
        Cap: round

      Inner ring (Habits):
        Diameter: 42px, stroke width: 4px
        Track: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
        Fill: #059669 (Emerald)
        Cap: round

      Center text:
        Percentage: Bebas Neue 400, 16px, #1A0533
        "done": DM Sans 400, 9px, #475569

      Completion animation (any ring hits 100%):
        Ring stroke-width pulses 6px -> 8px -> 6px over 300ms
        Gold shimmer travels along ring path (gradient mask animation, 500ms)
        Shimmer color: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(184,134,11,0.40), transparent)

      DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Track color is rgba(255,255,255,0.06) in dark.
        Ring colors are identical — they are vibrant enough on both backgrounds.
        The shimmer effect is more visible in dark mode (glow), subtler in light.

DAILY CONTENT CARD
-------------------
  Position: 20px below streak section
  Margin: 0 20px
  Width: calc(100% - 40px)

  Card:
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Border: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
    Border-radius: 16px
    Box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(26,5,51,0.06), 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
    Padding: 20px

  Category Badge (top-left inside card):
    Background: #6B21A8
    Border-radius: 100px
    Padding: 4px 12px
    Text: DM Sans 500, 11px, #FFFFFF, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.5px
    Example: "MAHABHARATA"

  Quote Text:
    Position: 16px below badge
    Font: Playfair Display 500, 18px / 26px, #1A0533
    Example: "The mind acts as both the friend and the enemy of the self."
    Max lines: 3 (ellipsis if longer)
    Style: italic

  Attribution:
    Position: 8px below quote
    Font: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569
    Text: "— Bhagavad Gita, Chapter 6"

  Share Button (bottom-right of card):
    Size: 36px x 36px circle
    Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
    Icon: share icon, 18px, #6B21A8
    Tap target: 44px x 44px (padded)

    Press state:
      Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.12)
      Scale: 0.95 -> 1.0 (spring, 200ms)

  SHARE CARD VARIANT (generated for social sharing):
    Background: #6B21A8 (deep violet — inverts for visual drama)
    Text: #B8860B (gold) for quote, #FFFFFF for attribution
    Logo: bottom-right, UNJYNX in #FFFFFF, small
    Border-radius: 16px
    Size: 1080x1080px (Instagram square)

    WHY inverted colors for share: Social feeds are visually noisy.
    A purple card with gold text stops the scroll. The light mode in-app
    card is calm/readable, but the share variant needs to POP externally.

  Swipe interaction:
    Swipe left: next quote (translateX, 300ms, curve-standard)
    Swipe right: previous quote
    Indicator dots: 4px circles, #6B21A8 active, rgba(107,33,168,0.20) inactive
    Position: centered, 8px below card

QUICK ACTIONS ROW
------------------
  Position: 20px below content card
  Padding: 0 20px
  Layout: horizontal scroll, 10px gap, no scrollbar visible
  Scroll padding: 20px start and end (peek effect)

  Quick Action Pill:
    Height: 40px
    Padding: 0 16px
    Background: rgba(255,255,255,0.70)
    Backdrop-filter: blur(6px)
    Border: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.10)
    Border-radius: 100px
    Box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)

    Icon: 18px, #6B21A8, left side
    Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, #1A0533, 8px right of icon
    Tap target: full pill area (min 44px height with padding)

    Active/Selected state:
      Background: #FFF8E1 (Gold Wash)
      Border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.20)
      Icon color: #B8860B
      Text color: #1A0533

    Press state:
      Scale: 0.97 -> 1.0 (100ms)
      Background: rgba(240,234,252,0.90)

  Actions (left to right):
    [+ New Task]  [Calendar]  [Focus]  [Projects]  [Habits]  [Analytics]

TASK SECTIONS
--------------
  Each section has a header + task card list.
  Position: 24px below quick actions
  Padding: 0 20px

  SECTION HEADER:
    Layout: horizontal, space-between
    Left: section title
    Right: count badge

    Title: Outfit 600, 18px, #1A0533
    Examples: "Today", "Upcoming", "Overdue"
    If "Overdue": title color = #E11D48

    Count badge:
      Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
      Border-radius: 100px
      Padding: 2px 10px
      Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, #6B21A8
      If overdue section: bg = rgba(225,29,72,0.08), text = #E11D48

    Margin-bottom: 12px

  TASK CARD:
    Width: 100%
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Border-radius: 14px
    Box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(26,5,51,0.05), 0 1px 3px rgba(26,5,51,0.03)
    Padding: 14px 16px
    Margin-bottom: 10px
    Min-height: 64px

    LEFT EDGE (Priority Indicator):
      Width: 3px
      Height: 100% (card height)
      Border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px (rounded on left corners only)
      Colors by priority:
        P1 (Critical): #B8860B (Gold)
        P2 (High):     #D97706 (Amber)
        P3 (Medium):   #6B21A8 (Violet)
        P4 (Low):      #475569 (Slate)

    OVERDUE VARIANT:
      Left border: 3px solid #E11D48
      Background: #FFFFFF tinted -> rgba(225,29,72,0.03) (barely pink)
      Entire card border: 1px solid rgba(225,29,72,0.08)
      WHY subtle pink: Just enough to signal urgency without alarming.
      Dark mode uses rgba(225,29,72,0.08) tint which glows more prominently.

    CHECKBOX (left, after priority edge):
      Position: left-aligned, vertically centered
      Size: 24px x 24px
      Unchecked:
        Border: 2px solid #6B21A8 at 40% opacity
        Background: transparent
        Border-radius: 6px
      Checked:
        Background: #B8860B (Gold fill)
        Border: 2px solid #B8860B
        Icon: white checkmark, 14px, stroke 2px
        Border-radius: 6px
      Animation on check:
        Scale: 1.0 -> 1.15 -> 1.0 (spring, 250ms)
        Gold burst: 6 particles, 3px, #B8860B at 60% opacity, radiate 16px then fade

    TASK TEXT (right of checkbox, 12px gap):
      Title: DM Sans 500, 15px / 20px, #1A0533
        Max 2 lines, ellipsis
        Completed: strikethrough with #6B21A8 line (not gray),
          text color: #94A3B8 (faded), line animates left -> right over 300ms
      Subtitle (due time, project, etc.):
        Font: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569
        Example: "2:30 PM - Work Project"
        Icon before text: 14px, matching color
        Margin-top: 2px

    TAGS (optional, below subtitle):
      Layout: horizontal wrap, 6px gap
      Tag pill:
        Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
        Border-radius: 100px
        Padding: 2px 8px
        Text: DM Sans 400, 11px, #6B21A8
        Max shown: 2, then "+N" pill

    RIGHT SIDE (chevron or time):
      If time-specific: DM Sans 500, 13px, #6B21A8
      If general: chevron icon, 16px, #94A3B8
      Tap: navigates to task detail

    PRESS STATE:
      Background: #F0EAFC (Surface)
      Box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(26,5,51,0.03) (reduced)
      Transition: 100ms

    DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Cards in dark use rgba(255,255,255,0.04) bg.
      Checkbox border is rgba(255,255,255,0.20) in dark.
      Priority stripe colors are identical — they are semantic, not theme-dependent.
      Strikethrough in dark is #8B5CF6 (lighter violet for visibility on dark bg).
      Light mode uses #6B21A8 strikethrough which is distinct on white without being heavy.

  EMPTY STATE (no tasks in section):
    Illustration: simple line art, 120px x 120px, #6B21A8 strokes
    Text: DM Sans 400, 15px, #475569, centered
    Example: "No tasks for today. Enjoy the calm."
    CTA: ghost button, "Add a task", DM Sans 500, 14px, #6B21A8
    Border: 1.5px solid #6B21A8, border-radius 10px, padding 8px 20px

AI WHISPER CARD
----------------
  Position: appears contextually (after first task section or at bottom)
  Margin: 20px horizontal, 16px vertical gap

  Card:
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Border: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
    Border-radius: 16px
    Box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(26,5,51,0.06), 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
    Padding: 16px

  Crystal Ball Icon:
    Position: left, vertically centered with first line of text
    Size: 36px x 36px
    Background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3B0764, #6B21A8)
    Border-radius: 10px
    Icon: crystal ball, 20px, #FFFFFF
    Box-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(59,7,100,0.20)

  Whisper Text (right of icon, 12px gap):
    Font: DM Sans 400, 14px / 20px, #1A0533
    Example: "You usually do deep work at 10 AM. Block 2 hours?"
    Max 2 lines

  Action Buttons (right side or below text):
    Layout: row, 8px gap
    "Yes": DM Sans 500, 13px, #B8860B, tap target 44px
    "Dismiss": DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569, tap target 44px

  Dismiss animation: card slides right (translateX 100%, 300ms) then height collapses (200ms)

BOTTOM NAVIGATION
------------------
  Position: fixed bottom
  Height: 64px + safe-area-bottom
  Background: rgba(255,255,255,0.85)
  Backdrop-filter: blur(12px) saturate(1.3)
  Border-top: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
  Box-shadow: 0 -2px 8px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)

  Items: 5 tabs, evenly distributed
  Tab:
    Icon: 24px, centered
    Label: DM Sans 500, 11px, centered, 4px below icon
    Tap target: full tab width x 64px

    Inactive: icon #475569, label #475569
    Active: icon #6B21A8, label #6B21A8
      Active indicator: pill behind icon, 48px x 28px, #EDE5F7, border-radius 100px
      Transition: 200ms curve-standard

  Tabs (left to right):
    Home (house) | Tasks (checkbox) | [FAB space] | Calendar (calendar) | Profile (person)

  Center FAB (floating above nav):
    Size: 56px x 56px
    Background: #B8860B
    Border-radius: 16px
    Box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(184,134,11,0.30), 0 2px 4px rgba(184,134,11,0.15)
    Icon: + (plus), 28px, #FFFFFF, stroke 2.5px
    Position: centered horizontally, vertically overlapping nav by 20px

    Press:
      Scale: 0.92 -> 1.0 (spring, 200ms)
      Background: #A07608

    DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: FAB is identical color (gold is brand-universal).
      Dark mode adds outer glow (0 0 24px rgba(184,134,11,0.35)).
      Light mode omits glow — gold on light already pops without artificial glow.


================================================================================
D1. QUICK CREATE (BOTTOM SHEET)
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Fastest path to create a task. NLP-powered parsing of natural language.
TRIGGER: Tap center FAB on bottom nav.
ANIMATION: Sheet slides up from bottom, 400ms, curve-decel.

OVERLAY
-------
  Background: rgba(26,5,51,0.20) (purple-tinted scrim — NOT black/gray)
  Tap outside: dismisses sheet
  Transition: opacity 0 -> 1, 300ms

SHEET
-----
  Background: #FFFFFF
  Border-radius: 24px 24px 0 0
  Box-shadow: 0 -8px 24px rgba(26,5,51,0.10), 0 -4px 12px rgba(26,5,51,0.05)
  Padding: 24px 20px (bottom = safe-area + 20px)
  Max-height: 70% of screen

  Drag handle:
    Position: top center, 8px from top
    Width: 36px, height: 4px
    Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.15)
    Border-radius: 2px

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Sheet bg is #1A0F2E in dark (deep purple).
    Shadow uses rgba(0,0,0,0.40). Scrim is rgba(0,0,0,0.50).
    Light mode uses clean white sheet with purple-tinted shadows for cohesion.

TEXT INPUT
----------
  Position: 20px below drag handle
  Width: 100%
  Min-height: 48px (expands with multiline)

  Field:
    Background: #FFFFFF (same as sheet, creating flush look)
    Border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.12) (underline style, not box)
    Padding: 8px 0

  Placeholder:
    Font: DM Sans 400, 16px, #94A3B8
    Text: "What do you need to do?"

  Input text:
    Font: DM Sans 400, 16px, #1A0533

  Focus state:
    Border-bottom: 2px solid #6B21A8
    Cursor: 2px wide, #B8860B (gold cursor — distinctive detail)
    Cursor blink: 1s interval

    WHY gold cursor: Small delight. The cursor is the user's point of action.
    Making it gold (the "action" color) subliminally reinforces progress.

NLP CHIPS (appear as user types, parsed entities)
--------------------------------------------------
  Position: 12px below input, horizontal wrap
  Layout: row wrap, 8px gap

  Category chip (e.g., "Work", "Personal"):
    Background: #6B21A8
    Border-radius: 100px
    Padding: 6px 12px
    Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, #FFFFFF
    Icon (optional): 14px, #FFFFFF, left of text, 6px gap
    Close button: 14px x, #FFFFFF at 60% opacity, right side, 6px gap

  Date/Time chip (e.g., "Tomorrow 3pm", "Friday"):
    Background: #FFF8E1 (Gold Wash)
    Border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.20)
    Border-radius: 100px
    Padding: 6px 12px
    Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, #B8860B
    Icon: clock/calendar 14px, #B8860B

  Priority chip:
    Background: transparent
    Border: 1.5px solid (priority color from 0.5 scale)
    Border-radius: 100px
    Padding: 6px 12px
    Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, (priority color)

  Chip appear animation:
    ScaleX: 0 -> 1, origin left, 200ms, curve-spring
    Opacity: 0 -> 1 over first 100ms

  Chip tap:
    Opens modifier (e.g., tap date chip -> date picker)

ADD BUTTON
----------
  Position: right side of input row (or bottom of sheet if chips present)
  Width: 100% if bottom position, 48px circle if inline
  Height: 48px (or 56px if full-width)

  Full-width variant:
    Background: #B8860B
    Border-radius: 12px
    Box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(184,134,11,0.20)
    Text: DM Sans 600, 15px, #FFFFFF — "Add Task"
    Margin-top: 16px

  Inline circular variant:
    Background: #B8860B
    Border-radius: 50%
    Size: 48px x 48px
    Icon: checkmark, 24px, #FFFFFF

  Disabled state (empty input):
    Opacity: 0.4
    No shadow

  Press:
    Scale: 0.95 -> 1.0 (150ms, spring)
    Background: #A07608

VOICE INPUT
-----------
  Trigger: microphone icon, 24px, #6B21A8, right side of input field
  Tap target: 44px x 44px

  Active state (recording):
    Icon: pulsing microphone, #E11D48 (recording red)
    Waveform bar below input:
      Height: 32px
      Bars: 40 vertical bars, 2px wide, 4px gap
      Base color: #6B21A8 (deep purple)
      Peak color: #B8860B (gold — for louder amplitudes)
      Amplitude mapping: bar heights 4px-28px
      Animation: real-time with 60fps spring interpolation

QUICK OPTION BUTTONS (below chips, above Add)
----------------------------------------------
  Layout: horizontal scroll, 8px gap
  Each:
    Icon: 18px, #6B21A8
    Text: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569
    Background: transparent
    Padding: 8px 12px
    Border: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
    Border-radius: 8px
    Tap target: min 44px height

  Options: [Priority] [Due Date] [Project] [Reminder] [Attach]


================================================================================
D2. TASK DETAIL
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Full view of a single task with all metadata, subtasks, activity.
ENTRY: Tap task card from home or list.
ANIMATION: Hero transition — card expands to full screen, 400ms, curve-standard.

HERO HEADER
------------
  Height: 120px (content area) + safe-area-top
  Background: #FFFFFF (default)

  DEADLINE TODAY VARIANT:
    Background: linear-gradient(180deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #FFF8E1 100%)
    WHY gold wash: Creates gentle urgency. Not alarming like red,
    but warm enough to say "this matters today."

  Back button:
    Position: top-left, safe-area + 12px, left 12px
    Size: 40px x 40px circle
    Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
    Icon: arrow-left, 20px, #1A0533
    Tap target: 44px x 44px

  More menu:
    Position: top-right, same vertical as back
    Size: 40px x 40px circle
    Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
    Icon: three dots vertical, 20px, #1A0533

  Task title:
    Position: 16px below back button row
    Padding: 0 20px
    Font: Outfit 700, 24px / 30px, #1A0533
    Max 2 lines, then scrollable

  Priority badge:
    Position: right of title or below, depending on title length
    Pill: padding 4px 10px, border-radius 100px
    Background: priority color at 10% opacity
    Text: DM Sans 600, 11px, priority color, uppercase

TASK METADATA SECTION
----------------------
  Position: below header, 16px gap
  Padding: 0 20px
  Background: #FFFFFF (continued from header, or starts the scroll body)

  Metadata rows (vertical stack, 16px gap):
    Each row:
      Height: 40px
      Layout: horizontal, icon + label + value
      Icon: 20px, #6B21A8, left
      Label: DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569, 12px right of icon
      Value: DM Sans 500, 14px, #1A0533, right-aligned

    Rows:
      Due Date: calendar icon, "Due", "Mar 10, 2026 at 3:00 PM"
      Project: folder icon, "Project", "Work — Q1 Launch"
      Priority: flag icon, "Priority", "P1 — Critical" (in priority color)
      Reminder: bell icon, "Reminder", "30 min before via WhatsApp"
      Repeat: repeat icon, "Repeat", "Every weekday"

    Divider between rows:
      Height: 1px
      Color: rgba(107,33,168,0.04)
      Margin: 0 (full width within padding)

DESCRIPTION FIELD
------------------
  Position: 16px below metadata
  Padding: 0 20px

  Label: DM Sans 500, 14px, #475569, margin-bottom 8px
  Content: DM Sans 400, 15px / 22px, #1A0533
  Placeholder (if empty): DM Sans 400, 15px, #94A3B8, "Add a description..."
  Tap: enters inline edit mode

  Inline edit:
    Underline: 2px solid #6B21A8 appears below text
    Cursor: 2px, #B8860B
    Save: auto-save on blur (debounced 500ms)

SUBTASKS
--------
  Position: 20px below description
  Padding: 0 20px

  Header:
    Text: "Subtasks" — Outfit 600, 16px, #1A0533
    Count: DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569 — "(3 of 5)"
    Add button: + icon, 20px, #6B21A8, right-aligned, tap 44px

  Progress bar (segment style):
    Position: 8px below header
    Height: 6px
    Background (track): #F0EAFC (lavender)
    Fill: #6B21A8 (deep violet)
    Segments: each subtask = proportional width, 2px gap between segments
    Completed segments: #6B21A8 solid
    Incomplete segments: #F0EAFC (track color)
    Border-radius: 3px (overall), 2px (segments)
    Animation: segment fills left -> right, 300ms per segment, curve-decel

  Subtask list:
    Layout: vertical, 8px gap, 12px below progress
    Each subtask:
      Height: 44px
      Layout: checkbox + text + drag handle

      Checkbox: same spec as main task checkbox (24px, purple ring, gold fill)
      Text: DM Sans 400, 14px, #1A0533
        Completed: strikethrough #6B21A8, color #94A3B8
      Drag handle: 6 dots (2x3 grid), 16px, #94A3B8, right side
        Visible: always (no hover dependency on mobile)
        Long-press to reorder: card lifts (shadow-lg, scale 1.02)

  Add subtask input:
    Below list, 8px gap
    Height: 40px
    Background: transparent
    Border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(107,33,168,0.12)
    Placeholder: DM Sans 400, 14px, #94A3B8, "+ Add subtask"
    Focus: border-bottom solid #6B21A8
    Submit: Enter key or checkmark button

ACTIVITY TIMELINE
------------------
  Position: 24px below subtasks
  Padding: 0 20px

  Header: "Activity" — Outfit 600, 16px, #1A0533

  Timeline:
    Layout: vertical, left-aligned
    Line: 2px solid #F0EAFC (lavender), left 10px from left edge, full height
    Dot: 8px circle, #6B21A8, centered on line, at each event
    Today dot: 8px circle, #B8860B (gold, current)

    Event entry:
      Position: right of dot, 16px gap from line
      Text: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569
      Bold part: DM Sans 600, 13px, #1A0533 (actor name, action)
      Time: DM Sans 400, 12px, #94A3B8, right-aligned or below
      Example: "Rahul marked subtask 'Research' as complete - 2h ago"

    Gap between events: 20px


================================================================================
D3. EDIT TASK
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Full editing of task. Same layout as D2 but all fields are interactive.
ENTRY: "Edit" from task detail more menu, or long-press task card.

KEY DIFFERENCES FROM D2 (TASK DETAIL)
---------------------------------------
  1. All text fields are editable inline (not read-only)
  2. Metadata values are tappable and open pickers
  3. Save/Cancel buttons in app bar
  4. Visual "edit mode" indicators

APP BAR (edit mode):
  Left: "Cancel" — DM Sans 500, 15px, #475569, tap 44px
  Center: "Edit Task" — Outfit 600, 18px, #1A0533
  Right: "Save" — DM Sans 600, 15px, #B8860B, tap 44px
    Disabled (no changes): opacity 0.4
    Enabled: full opacity + gold underline on press

EDITABLE FIELDS
-----------------
  Title:
    Field: Outfit 700, 24px, #1A0533
    Background: transparent
    Focus: 2px underline #6B21A8
    Cursor: #B8860B

  Description:
    Multi-line text area
    Min-height: 80px
    Focus: 2px underline #6B21A8
    Cursor: #B8860B

DATE / TIME PICKER
-------------------
  Triggered by tapping Due Date metadata row
  Style: Material 3 date picker, custom themed

  Calendar header:
    Background: #F8F5FF
    Month/year: Outfit 600, 18px, #1A0533
    Arrows: 24px, #6B21A8

  Day cells:
    Size: 40px x 40px
    Font: DM Sans 400, 14px
    Default: #1A0533
    Other month: #94A3B8
    Today: #B8860B text, no fill
    Selected: #6B21A8 circle fill, #FFFFFF text
    Range (if applicable): #EDE5F7 fill between, endpoints #6B21A8

  Time picker:
    Scrolling wheels or input fields
    Accent: #6B21A8

PRIORITY SELECTOR
------------------
  Triggered by tapping Priority metadata row
  Style: bottom sheet or inline selector

  Layout: 4 options in a row
  Each:
    Size: 72px x 72px
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Border: 1.5px solid rgba(priority-color, 0.20)
    Border-radius: 12px
    Selected: border 2px solid #B8860B, background: #FFF8E1

    Icon: flag, 24px, priority color, centered
    Label: DM Sans 500, 11px, priority color, below icon

    P1: #B8860B — "Critical"
    P2: #D97706 — "High"
    P3: #6B21A8 — "Medium"
    P4: #475569 — "Low"

UNSAVED CHANGES INDICATOR
---------------------------
  If changes detected:
    Subtle gold dot (6px, #B8860B) next to "Save" text
    Pulsing animation: opacity 0.5 -> 1.0, 1.5s loop


================================================================================
D4. KANBAN BOARD
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Visual project/task organization in columns.
ENTRY: Task view toggle or project view.

BACKGROUND: #F8F5FF

COLUMN STRUCTURE
-----------------
  Layout: horizontal scroll of columns
  Column width: 280px (fixed)
  Column gap: 12px
  Padding: 20px (first column), 20px (last column right)

  Column:
    Background: #F0EAFC at top (header), transparent body
    Border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0 (header)
    Full height: remaining screen below app bar

  Column Header:
    Height: 48px
    Background: #EDE5F7
    Border-radius: 16px 16px 0 0
    Padding: 0 16px
    Layout: horizontal, space-between

    Title: DM Sans 600, 15px, #1A0533
    Count: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569, right side
    Add button: + icon, 20px, #6B21A8, right of count, 8px gap, tap 44px

    Column types + header indicators:
      "To Do": left 3px border #475569
      "In Progress": left 3px border #6B21A8
      "Review": left 3px border #D97706
      "Done": left 3px border #059669

KANBAN CARDS
-------------
  Width: 100% of column (minus 16px padding each side)
  Background: #FFFFFF
  Border-radius: 12px
  Box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.05)
  Padding: 12px
  Margin-bottom: 8px

  Title: DM Sans 500, 14px, #1A0533, max 2 lines
  Due date: DM Sans 400, 12px, #475569, 4px below title
  Priority: 3px left border (priority color)
  Assignee avatar: 24px circle, bottom-right
  Tag pills: same as home task card spec

DRAG INTERACTION
-----------------
  Long-press to pick up (300ms):
    Card lifts: scale 1.00 -> 1.02, shadow-xl
    Background: #FFFFFF (unchanged — shadow creates depth)
    Opacity of remaining cards: 0.6

  Dragging:
    Card follows finger with 2px offset (no sticking to finger exactly)
    Source column: gap where card was remains (placeholder 4px height, #F0EAFC)
    Target column: insertion line appears (2px, #6B21A8) between cards

  Column hover glow:
    When dragging over a column, the column header bg lightens:
    #EDE5F7 -> #F8F5FF (0.3s transition)
    Subtle: rgba(107,33,168,0.03) overlay on entire column body

  Drop:
    Card animates to position (200ms, curve-spring)
    Shadow returns to shadow-sm
    Scale returns to 1.00
    Haptic feedback: light impact

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Drag shadow uses glow (rgba(107,33,168,0.20)) in dark.
    Light mode uses deeper purple-tinted shadow (more natural, less neon).
    Column hover in dark = column bg brightens more dramatically (0.08 -> 0.15 opacity).


================================================================================
D5. LIST VIEW
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Dense, scannable task list. Optimized for many tasks.
ENTRY: View toggle from tasks screen.

BACKGROUND: #F8F5FF

SECTION HEADERS
----------------
  Background: #F0EAFC
  Height: 36px
  Padding: 0 20px
  Text: DM Sans 600, 13px, #1A0533, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.5px
  Sticky: yes, sticks below app bar on scroll
  Border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.06)

TASK ROWS
----------
  Width: 100%
  Height: 60px
  Background: #FFFFFF (alternating with #F8F5FF for readability — optional)
  Padding: 0 20px
  Layout: horizontal — checkbox | text column | time/status | chevron

  Checkbox: same spec as home task card (24px, purple ring, gold fill)
  Title: DM Sans 400, 15px, #1A0533
  Subtitle: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569
  Time: DM Sans 500, 13px, #6B21A8, right side
  Chevron: 16px, #94A3B8, rightmost

DIVIDERS
---------
  Height: 1px
  Color: rgba(107,33,168,0.04) — very subtle lavender
  Full width (no inset for cleaner look)

SWIPE ACTIONS
--------------
  Swipe Left (Delete):
    Reveal background: #E11D48
    Icon: trash, 24px, #FFFFFF
    Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, #FFFFFF — "Delete"
    Threshold: 80px to trigger, then auto-complete

  Swipe Right (Complete):
    Reveal background: #059669
    Icon: checkmark-circle, 24px, #FFFFFF
    Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, #FFFFFF — "Done"
    Threshold: 80px to trigger

  Swipe physics:
    Resistance: 0.8x beyond threshold (feels like pulling a rubber band)
    Snap back: 300ms, curve-standard
    Trigger animation: row slides fully out (400ms), then collapses height (200ms)

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Swipe reveal colors are identical (semantic colors).
    The row bg in dark is rgba(255,255,255,0.04), creating more contrast with reveal.
    Light mode row bg is white, so the color reveal is equally dramatic.


================================================================================
D6. PRIORITY MATRIX (Eisenhower)
================================================================================

PURPOSE: 2x2 grid organizing tasks by urgency and importance.
ENTRY: View toggle or dedicated button.

BACKGROUND: #F8F5FF

MATRIX GRID
-------------
  Position: below app bar, full remaining height
  Padding: 12px
  Gap between quadrants: 8px
  Layout: 2x2 CSS grid

  Each quadrant:
    Flex: 1 (equal size)
    Border-radius: 16px
    Padding: 12px
    Min-height: 50% of available height - 4px gap

  Quadrant styling:
    Q1 — Urgent + Important (top-left):
      Background: #FFF8E1 (Gold Wash)
      Border: 1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.12)
      Label: "DO FIRST" — Outfit 600, 12px, #B8860B, uppercase

    Q2 — Not Urgent + Important (top-right):
      Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.03) (barely purple)
      Border: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
      Label: "SCHEDULE" — Outfit 600, 12px, #6B21A8, uppercase

    Q3 — Urgent + Not Important (bottom-left):
      Background: rgba(217,119,6,0.03) (barely amber)
      Border: 1px solid rgba(217,119,6,0.06)
      Label: "DELEGATE" — Outfit 600, 12px, #D97706, uppercase

    Q4 — Not Urgent + Not Important (bottom-right):
      Background: rgba(71,85,105,0.03) (barely slate)
      Border: 1px solid rgba(71,85,105,0.06)
      Label: "ELIMINATE" — Outfit 600, 12px, #475569, uppercase

  Labels:
    Position: top-left of each quadrant, 12px from edges
    All labels: letter-spacing 1px

  Axis labels:
    "URGENT ->" along top: DM Sans 500, 11px, #94A3B8, centered above top row
    "IMPORTANT (up arrow)" along left: DM Sans 500, 11px, #94A3B8, rotated -90deg, centered left

  Quadrant dividers:
    Vertical center line: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
    Horizontal center line: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)

TASKS IN QUADRANTS
-------------------
  Mini task card:
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Border-radius: 8px
    Box-shadow: 0 1px 3px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
    Padding: 8px 10px
    Margin-bottom: 6px

    Text: DM Sans 400, 13px, #1A0533, max 1 line, ellipsis
    Priority dot: 6px circle, priority color, right of text

  Drag between quadrants: same drag spec as Kanban (lift, shadow, drop)
  Max visible per quadrant: 5, then "View N more" link
    Link: DM Sans 500, 12px, #6B21A8


================================================================================
D7. BATCH OPERATIONS
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Multi-select tasks for bulk actions (complete, delete, move, re-prioritize).
TRIGGER: Long-press any task card, or "Select" button in list view.

SELECTION STATE
----------------
  Entering batch mode:
    App bar transforms: title -> "N selected" (Outfit 600, 18px, #1A0533)
    App bar left: "Cancel" text button (DM Sans 500, 15px, #475569)
    App bar right: "Select All" (DM Sans 500, 15px, #6B21A8)

  Selected task card:
    Background: #FFF8E1 (Gold Wash)
    Border: 2px solid #B8860B
    Box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(184,134,11,0.12)
    Checkbox: replaced with gold-filled circle checkmark
    Scale: 1.0 (no scale change — border/color is sufficient)
    Transition: all 150ms, curve-standard

  Unselected task card (in batch mode):
    Same as normal but with unchecked selection circle
    Selection circle: 24px, 2px border #6B21A8 at 30% opacity
    Replaces normal checkbox

  Select All checkbox:
    Same 24px spec, #6B21A8 border
    Checked: #6B21A8 fill, white checkmark (not gold — to differentiate from individual)

ACTION BAR
-----------
  Position: fixed bottom (above bottom nav, or replacing it)
  Height: 64px + safe-area-bottom
  Background: rgba(255,255,255,0.90)
  Backdrop-filter: blur(12px)
  Border-top: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
  Box-shadow: 0 -4px 12px rgba(26,5,51,0.06)
  Padding: 0 20px

  Actions (evenly distributed):
    Complete: checkmark-circle, 24px, #059669
    Move: folder-move, 24px, #6B21A8
    Priority: flag, 24px, #D97706
    Delete: trash, 24px, #E11D48

    Each action:
      Layout: vertical — icon + label
      Label: DM Sans 500, 11px, matching icon color
      Tap target: 64px x 64px
      Press: scale 0.90 -> 1.0 (100ms, spring)

  Delete confirmation:
    Modal dialog: white card, centered, shadow-2xl
    Title: "Delete N tasks?" — Outfit 600, 18px, #1A0533
    Body: DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569
    Cancel: ghost button, #475569
    Delete: #E11D48 bg, #FFFFFF text, border-radius 10px


================================================================================
E1. SEARCH
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Find any task, project, or content quickly.
ENTRY: Search icon in app bar or quick action pill.

BACKGROUND: #F8F5FF

SEARCH BAR
-----------
  Position: top, safe-area + 12px, padding 0 20px
  Height: 48px
  Width: calc(100% - 40px)
  Background: #FFFFFF
  Border: 1.5px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.10)
  Border-radius: 12px
  Box-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
  Padding: 0 16px

  Search icon: 20px, #6B21A8, left
  Input: DM Sans 400, 15px, #1A0533, 12px right of icon
  Placeholder: DM Sans 400, 15px, #94A3B8 — "Search tasks, projects..."
  Clear button (when input has text): 18px x circle, #475569, right side

  Focus state:
    Border: 1.5px solid #6B21A8
    Box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(107,33,168,0.08), 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)

  Auto-focus on entry: keyboard opens immediately

RECENT SEARCHES (when input is empty)
---------------------------------------
  Position: 16px below search bar
  Padding: 0 20px

  Section title: DM Sans 600, 13px, #475569, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.5px
  "RECENT SEARCHES"
  Clear all: right-aligned, DM Sans 500, 13px, #E11D48

  Recent items (vertical list, 4px gap):
    Each:
      Height: 44px
      Layout: horizontal — clock icon + text + remove
      Clock icon: 16px, #6B21A8 at 40% opacity
      Text: DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569, 12px right of icon
      Remove (x): 16px, #94A3B8, right side, tap 44px
      Tap: populates search bar and triggers search

  Max shown: 5 recent searches

SEARCH RESULTS (live as user types)
------------------------------------
  Position: 12px below search bar (replacing recent searches)
  Padding: 0 20px

  Results use standard task card styling (from C1 task card spec)
  Highlighted matches: text portions matching query
    Background: #FFF8E1 (Gold Wash) on matching characters
    Text color: #1A0533 (unchanged — gold bg highlights it)
    WHY gold highlight: Consistent with selection/active metaphor.
    Yellow highlighter on white paper is universally understood.

  Group headers (if results span types):
    "Tasks" / "Projects" / "Notes"
    Font: DM Sans 600, 13px, #475569, uppercase
    Margin: 16px top, 8px bottom

  Empty state (no results):
    Position: centered in results area
    Illustration: magnifying glass with question mark, 80px, #6B21A8 strokes
    Text: "No results for 'query'" — DM Sans 400, 15px, #475569
    Suggestion: "Try different keywords" — DM Sans 400, 13px, #94A3B8


================================================================================
E2. FILTERS
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Narrow task list by criteria.
ENTRY: Filter icon button near search or in list/board views.

LAYOUT: Bottom sheet or side panel.

FILTER CHIPS (top of filter panel)
-----------------------------------
  Layout: horizontal wrap, 8px gap
  Padding: 16px 20px

  Chip (inactive):
    Background: transparent
    Border: 1.5px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.15)
    Border-radius: 100px
    Padding: 8px 16px
    Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, #6B21A8
    Icon (optional): 16px, #6B21A8, left, 6px gap

  Chip (active):
    Background: #6B21A8
    Border: 1.5px solid #6B21A8
    Text: DM Sans 500, 13px, #FFFFFF
    Icon: 16px, #FFFFFF
    Close x: 14px, #FFFFFF at 70%, right side

  Chip types: Priority, Due Date, Project, Status, Tags, Assignee

DATE RANGE PICKER
------------------
  Calendar: same themed spec as D3 date picker
  Accent color: #6B21A8
  Range fill: #EDE5F7 between start and end dates
  Start/End circles: #6B21A8 fill, #FFFFFF text
  Quick options: "Today", "This Week", "This Month", "Overdue"
    Each: ghost chip, 1.5px #6B21A8 border, tap toggles

CLEAR ALL BUTTON
-----------------
  Position: top-right of filter panel
  Text: "Clear All" — DM Sans 500, 14px, #E11D48
  Tap target: 44px height
  Only visible when filters are active

APPLY / RESULTS COUNT
----------------------
  Bottom of panel
  Text: "Show N results" — DM Sans 600, 15px
  Button: full width, #B8860B bg, #FFFFFF text, border-radius 12px
  Height: 52px
  Updates count in real-time as filters change


================================================================================
E3. SEARCH RESULTS (FULL PAGE)
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Display filtered/searched results with sorting.
ENTRY: After applying filters or submitting search.

RESULTS LIST
--------------
  Same as D5 List View spec for task rows
  Match highlighting:
    Background: #FFF8E1 on matched text characters
    No additional text color change — gold wash is sufficient
    Border-radius on highlight: 2px

SORT OPTIONS (top bar)
-----------------------
  Layout: horizontal scroll pills below search/filter bar
  Options: "Relevance", "Due Date", "Priority", "Created", "A-Z"
  Active: #6B21A8 fill, #FFFFFF text
  Inactive: transparent, #6B21A8 border, #6B21A8 text

EMPTY STATE
-----------
  Illustration: purple line art, 120px x 120px
    Content: open box with floating question marks
    Stroke: #6B21A8 at 40% opacity, 2px
  Title: "No matches found" — Outfit 600, 18px, #1A0533
  Body: "Try adjusting your search or filters" — DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569
  CTA: "Clear Filters" — ghost button, #6B21A8

RESULTS COUNT BAR
------------------
  Height: 36px
  Background: #F0EAFC
  Padding: 0 20px
  Text: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569
  Example: "24 tasks found - sorted by relevance"


================================================================================
F1. CALENDAR VIEW
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Month/week/day calendar with task heatmap and scheduling.
ENTRY: Calendar tab in bottom nav.

BACKGROUND: #F8F5FF

CALENDAR HEADER
-----------------
  Height: 56px
  Padding: 0 20px
  Layout: horizontal — back arrow | month/year | forward arrow | view toggle

  Month/Year: Outfit 700, 20px, #1A0533 ("March 2026")
  Arrows: 24px, #6B21A8, tap 44px each
  View toggle (right): segmented control
    Options: "Month" | "Week" | "Day"
    Each segment: 60px wide, 32px tall
    Active: #6B21A8 bg, #FFFFFF text, border-radius 8px
    Inactive: transparent, #475569 text
    Container: border 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.10), border-radius 10px

MONTH HEATMAP VIEW
--------------------
  Grid: 7 columns (Sun-Sat), ~5 rows
  Weekday headers:
    Font: DM Sans 500, 12px, #475569, uppercase
    Height: 32px
    Letter-spacing: 0.5px
    Alignment: center each column

  Day cells:
    Size: (screen-width - 40px) / 7 = ~48px at 375px screen
    Aspect: square (48x48)
    Border-radius: 12px
    Margin: 2px
    Content: day number centered

    Day number:
      Font: DM Sans 500, 14px
      Current month: #1A0533
      Other months: #475569 at 40% opacity

    TODAY cell:
      Background: #FFF8E1 (Gold Wash)
      Border: 1.5px solid #B8860B
      Day number: #B8860B, font-weight 700

    Heatmap (task count -> background):
      0 tasks:    #F8F5FF (base, essentially invisible)
      1-2 tasks:  #EDE5F7 (lightest lavender)
      3-5 tasks:  #D0BCFF (medium lavender)
      6-9 tasks:  #6B21A8 (deep violet) — day number becomes #FFFFFF
      10+ tasks:  #B8860B (gold) — day number becomes #FFFFFF

      WHY this progression: Lavender -> violet -> gold creates a natural intensity
      ramp that stays on-brand. Gold for 10+ rewards productive days visually.

    Selected cell:
      Border: 2px solid #6B21A8
      Background: heatmap color preserved
      Content below calendar updates to show that day's tasks

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Heatmap colors are more saturated in dark
    (they need to be, since dark bg absorbs light). Same progression conceptually.

TASK LIST BELOW CALENDAR (selected day)
-----------------------------------------
  Position: below calendar grid, 16px gap
  Divider: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.06), full width

  Header: selected day in full format
    "Tuesday, March 10, 2026"
    Font: DM Sans 600, 14px, #475569
    Padding: 12px 20px 8px

  Task list: same card spec as C1 home task cards
  Empty state: DM Sans 400, 14px, #94A3B8, "No tasks this day", centered

DAY VIEW (TIME GRID)
----------------------
  Hour rows: 24 rows (midnight to midnight)
  Row height: 60px (1 hour)
  Time label: DM Sans 400, 12px, #94A3B8, left-aligned, 20px from left
  Grid line: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.04) at each hour

  CURRENT TIME LINE:
    Color: #B8860B (rich gold)
    Height: 2px
    Full width (minus left time label area)
    Left dot: 8px circle, #B8860B, on the left edge
    Position: calculated from current time
    Animation: updates every minute (no visible animation, just repositions)

    WHY gold time line: Gold = NOW, the present moment. The user's attention
    is naturally drawn to where they are in time. Gold makes it scannable.

  TASK BLOCKS:
    Each task that has a specific time slot:
    Background: project-color at 15% opacity
    Left border: 2px solid project-color (full saturation)
    Border-radius: 8px (right corners) 0px (left — border IS the left edge)
    Height: proportional to duration (60px per hour)
    Margin-left: 56px (after time labels)
    Padding: 8px 12px

    Title: DM Sans 500, 13px, #1A0533
    Time: DM Sans 400, 12px, #475569
    Max 2 lines, then ellipsis

    Overlapping tasks: stacked horizontally, 4px offset to the right
    Each subsequent overlap is 40px narrower with 4px right offset

WEEK VIEW
----------
  Header: 7 day columns with abbreviated day names
    Font: DM Sans 500, 12px, #475569, centered
    Below: day number, DM Sans 600, 14px, #1A0533
    Today column: day number in gold circle (#B8860B bg, #FFFFFF text)

  Time grid: same as day view but columns are 1/7 screen width
  Task blocks: abbreviated (title only, 11px font)
  Vertical scroll: independent per column


================================================================================
F2. TIME BLOCKING VIEW
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Plan time blocks for deep work, meetings, breaks.
ENTRY: Sub-view within calendar day view, or dedicated focus feature.

BACKGROUND: #F8F5FF

TIME SLOT TRACK
-----------------
  Layout: vertical time grid (same structure as F1 day view)
  Hour row height: 60px
  Track background: #F0EAFC (lavender) — continuous vertical stripe
  Track width: calc(100% - 76px) (leaving space for time labels + right padding)
  Track left margin: 56px
  Track right margin: 20px

BLOCKED TIME SEGMENTS
-----------------------
  Each time block:
    Background: project-color at 20% opacity
    Left border: 3px solid project-color (full saturation)
    Border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0
    Padding: 8px 12px

    Title: DM Sans 500, 14px, #1A0533
    Duration: DM Sans 400, 12px, #475569
    Category icon: 16px, project-color, left of title

  Free time (unblocked):
    Background: transparent (shows lavender track)
    Dashed border: 1px dashed rgba(107,33,168,0.10) at top/bottom
    Center text (optional): DM Sans 400, 12px, #94A3B8, "Available"
    Tap: opens quick block creation

CURRENT TIME MARKER
---------------------
  Same as F1: 2px #B8860B horizontal line + 8px gold dot on left
  Always visible, scrolls with time grid

DRAG HANDLES (for resizing blocks)
------------------------------------
  Position: top and bottom edges of each block
  Visual: row of 3 dots (each 4px circle), centered horizontally
    Color: #6B21A8 at 40% opacity
    Spacing: 4px between dots
  Tap target: 44px height (extends beyond visible dots)

  Drag behavior:
    Handle follows finger (constrained to vertical axis)
    Block resizes in 15-minute increments (15px per increment)
    Snap lines appear: thin #6B21A8 line at 15-min boundaries
    Duration label updates live: e.g., "1h 30m" -> "1h 45m"

BLOCK CREATION (tap on free time)
-----------------------------------
  Quick creation bottom sheet (mini version of D1):
    Title input
    Block type selector: [Focus] [Meeting] [Break] [Personal]
    Each type: color-coded pill
    Start/End time: DM Sans 500, 14px, #1A0533
    Save: #B8860B button


================================================================================
F3. POMODORO TIMER
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Focus timer with ambient environment.
ENTRY: Focus quick action or dedicated tab.

BACKGROUND: #F8F5FF with subtle warm tint when timer is active

TIMER RING (CENTER DOMINANT)
------------------------------
  Position: centered horizontally, upper third of screen
  Outer diameter: 280px
  Ring stroke: 10px

  Track:
    Color: #F0EAFC (lavender)
    Stroke-linecap: round

  Fill (progress):
    Color: #B8860B (Gold)
    Stroke-linecap: round
    Direction: clockwise from top (12 o'clock)
    Animation: smooth progression (updates every second)

  BREAK MODE:
    Track: #F0EAFC (unchanged)
    Fill: #059669 (Emerald green)
    Background wash: #FFF8E1 (warm gold wash on the full screen background)
    WHY warm wash on break: Creates a noticeable atmosphere shift.
    "Work" = clean lavender. "Break" = warm gold. Subliminally different.

  Center content:
    Time remaining: Bebas Neue 400, 64px, #1A0533
      Format: "25:00" or "04:37"
    Session label: DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569
      "Focus Session" or "Short Break" or "Long Break"
    Session count: DM Sans 500, 13px, #6B21A8
      "Session 3 of 4"

CONTROL BUTTONS
-----------------
  Position: centered, 40px below timer ring
  Layout: horizontal, 24px gap

  Play/Pause (center, primary):
    Size: 64px x 64px
    Background: #B8860B
    Border-radius: 50%
    Box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(184,134,11,0.25)
    Icon: play (triangle) or pause (two bars), 28px, #FFFFFF

    Press: scale 0.92 -> 1.0 (spring, 200ms)

  Reset (left):
    Size: 48px x 48px
    Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
    Border-radius: 50%
    Icon: reset/rewind, 22px, #6B21A8

  Skip (right):
    Size: 48px x 48px
    Background: rgba(107,33,168,0.06)
    Border-radius: 50%
    Icon: skip-forward, 22px, #6B21A8

AMBIENT PARTICLES
------------------
  Small floating particles that create a calming atmosphere.
  Opacity: 20% (vs 30% in dark mode)
  WHY lower opacity: On light backgrounds, particles at 30% are distracting.
  20% makes them subliminal — felt, not studied.

  RAIN mode:
    Particle type: small streaks (2px x 8px), falling at 15deg angle
    Color: #334155 at 20% opacity (deep blue-gray)
    Count: 40 particles
    Speed: vary 2-5 seconds to traverse screen
    Wind: subtle horizontal drift, +/-2px

  FOREST mode:
    Particle type: small leaf shapes (6px x 4px), gentle floating
    Color: #166534 at 20% opacity (deep green)
    Count: 25 particles
    Movement: sinusoidal drift, 0.5Hz, amplitude 8px
    Rotation: slow spin, 360deg over 8 seconds

  CAFE mode:
    Particle type: circles (3-5px), floating upward (like steam)
    Color: #9A3412 at 20% opacity (deep brown-orange)
    Count: 20 particles
    Movement: rise slowly, slight horizontal wobble
    Lifespan: 4 seconds, fade out in last 1 second

  DARK MODE DIFFERENCE: Particles in dark are lighter colors at 30% opacity
    (they need to be brighter to be visible on dark bg). Light mode uses
    darker tints at lower opacity — the inverse strategy for the same effect.

LINKED TASK
-----------
  Position: below controls, 32px gap
  Card: white bg, purple shadow spec (same as AI whisper card)
  Content: "Working on: [Task Title]"
  Font: DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569 (prefix), DM Sans 500, 14px, #1A0533 (title)
  Tap: opens task detail
  Close: 16px x icon, right side, #94A3B8

SESSION SETTINGS (below linked task)
--------------------------------------
  Layout: row of 3 settings
  Each: vertical stack, centered
    Label: DM Sans 400, 12px, #475569
    Value: DM Sans 600, 16px, #1A0533
    Stepper: - / + buttons, 28px, #6B21A8 border circles

  Settings: Focus (25 min), Break (5 min), Long Break (15 min)


================================================================================
F4. FOCUS SESSIONS
================================================================================

PURPOSE: Track and display completed focus sessions, current session status.
ENTRY: Sub-tab in Focus/Pomodoro area, or from home screen quick action.

BACKGROUND: #F8F5FF

SESSION CARDS
--------------
  Layout: vertical list, 12px gap
  Padding: 0 20px

  Card:
    Background: rgba(255,255,255,0.65) (glass effect)
    Backdrop-filter: blur(8px) saturate(1.2)
    Border: 1px solid rgba(107,33,168,0.08)
    Border-radius: 16px
    Box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(26,5,51,0.06), 0 2px 4px rgba(26,5,51,0.04)
    Padding: 16px

    Layout: horizontal — left info | right duration

    Left side:
      Task title: DM Sans 500, 15px, #1A0533
      Time range: DM Sans 400, 13px, #475569
        "10:00 AM — 10:25 AM"
      Tags: mini pills (same spec as task card tags)

    Right side:
      Duration: Bebas Neue 400, 32px, #1A0533
        "25m" or "1h 15m"
      Format: hours use "h", minutes use "m"

ACTIVE SESSION INDICATOR
--------------------------
  If a session is currently active, the first card shows:

  Active card:
    Border: 1.5px solid #B8860B (gold border)
    Background: rgba(255,248,225,0.50) (gold wash glass)

    Pulsing dot:
      Size: 10px
      Color: #B8860B
      Position: top-right of card, 12px from edges
      Animation: opacity 0.4 -> 1.0 -> 0.4, 2s loop, ease-in-out
      Glow: 0 0 8px rgba(184,134,11,0.30) pulses with opacity

    Live timer: Bebas Neue 400, 32px, #1A0533 (updates every second)
    Label: DM Sans 400, 12px, #B8860B, "IN PROGRESS"

SESSION STATS (top of page, before list)
-------------------------------------------
  Layout: 3 stat cards in a row, 12px gap
  Each stat:
    Width: (screen-width - 40px - 24px) / 3
    Height: 80px
    Background: #FFFFFF
    Border-radius: 12px
    Box-shadow: shadow-sm
    Padding: 12px
    Layout: vertical center

    Number: Bebas Neue 400, 28px, #1A0533
    Label: DM Sans 400, 11px, #475569
    Unit: DM Sans 400, 11px, #475569

  Stats:
    1. Total today: "4" + "sessions"
    2. Focus time: "1h 40m" + "focused"
    3. Streak: "7" + "day streak"

DATE GROUPING
--------------
  Sessions grouped by date
  Date header:
    Text: "Today", "Yesterday", "March 8, 2026"
    Font: DM Sans 600, 13px, #475569, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.5px
    Padding: 16px 20px 8px
    Background: transparent
    Sticky: yes

EMPTY STATE
-----------
  Illustration: stopwatch outline, 100px, #6B21A8 strokes at 30% opacity
  Title: "No focus sessions yet" — Outfit 600, 18px, #1A0533
  Body: "Start a Pomodoro timer to track your deep work" — DM Sans 400, 14px, #475569
  CTA: "Start Focus" — gold button, same spec as login CTA but smaller (48px height)


================================================================================
APPENDIX A: LIGHT <-> DARK MODE TRANSITION
================================================================================

When user toggles theme (settings or system automatic):

TRANSITION ANIMATION:
  Type: circular reveal from toggle switch position
  Duration: 500ms
  Easing: curve-standard
  The new theme colors expand in a circle from the toggle point
  All elements crossfade within the reveal circle

COLOR MAPPING TABLE (summary):
  +-----------------+-------------------+---------------------+
  | Token           | Light             | Dark                |
  +-----------------+-------------------+---------------------+
  | bg-primary      | #F8F5FF           | #0A0118             |
  | bg-surface      | #F0EAFC           | #1A0F2E             |
  | bg-card         | #FFFFFF           | rgba(255,255,255,   |
  |                 |                   |  0.04)              |
  | text-primary    | #1A0533           | #F8F5FF             |
  | text-secondary  | #6B21A8           | #B794F6             |
  | text-tertiary   | #475569           | #94A3B8             |
  | brand-gold      | #B8860B           | #D4A017             |
  | shadow-base     | rgba(26,5,51,x)   | rgba(0,0,0,x)      |
  | glass-bg        | rgba(255,255,255, | rgba(26,5,51,       |
  |                 |  0.65)            |  0.40)              |
  | glass-border    | rgba(107,33,168,  | rgba(255,255,255,   |
  |                 |  0.08)            |  0.06)              |
  | divider         | rgba(107,33,168,  | rgba(255,255,255,   |
  |                 |  0.04)            |  0.04)              |
  | semantic colors | SAME              | SAME (slightly      |
  |                 |                   |  brighter variants) |
  +-----------------+-------------------+---------------------+


================================================================================
APPENDIX B: ACCESSIBILITY NOTES
================================================================================

CONTRAST RATIOS (verified against WCAG 2.1 AA):
  - #1A0533 on #F8F5FF: 17.51:1 (AAA pass — exceeds 7:1)
  - #6B21A8 on #F8F5FF: 8.20:1  (AAA pass — exceeds 7:1)
  - #475569 on #F8F5FF: 6.10:1  (AA pass — exceeds 4.5:1)
  - #FFFFFF on #B8860B: 4.80:1  (AA pass — exceeds 4.5:1 for large text)
  - #FFFFFF on #6B21A8: 7.84:1  (AAA pass — exceeds 7:1)
  - #FFFFFF on #E11D48: 4.53:1  (AA pass — barely, use bold/large only)
  - #B8860B on #FFF8E1: 5.12:1  (AA pass)

TOUCH TARGETS:
  - ALL interactive elements: minimum 44px x 44px
  - Buttons with visual size < 44px: invisible padding extends hit area
  - Adjacent targets: minimum 8px gap between tap zones

MOTION:
  - All animations respect prefers-reduced-motion
  - Reduced motion: instant state changes, no particles, no shimmer
  - Timer still updates (functional, not decorative)

SCREEN READER:
  - All icons have semantic labels
  - Task cards: full context announced (title, project, priority, due)
  - Progress rings: percentage announced
  - Swipe actions: labeled for VoiceOver/TalkBack


================================================================================
APPENDIX C: RESPONSIVE BREAKPOINTS
================================================================================

  Mobile portrait (375-414px): default spec above
  Mobile landscape (667-896px): 2-column task grid, timer beside controls
  Tablet portrait (768-834px): sidebar nav, wider cards (max 560px)
  Tablet landscape (1024-1194px): persistent sidebar + 2-panel layout
  Foldable inner (1080px+): adaptive 2-panel with fold-aware layout

  All specs above are mobile-first (375px base). Scale rules:
  - Typography: unchanged up to tablet, +2px on tablet landscape
  - Spacing: 1.25x on tablet, 1.5x on large tablet
  - Card widths: max-width constraints prevent over-stretching
  - FAB: position adjusts to right side on tablet landscape


================================================================================
END OF LIGHT MODE DESIGN SPECIFICATION — PART 1 (SCREENS A-F)
================================================================================

